response.original_title: Stevie Nicks & Lady Antebellum: CMT Crossroads
response.overview: Meeting and collaborating for the first time on the CMT Crossroads stage in Los Angeles, Nicks and Lady Antebellum share harmonies and stories.  Setlist:  01. Intro  02. Edge of Seventeen  03. Love Don't Live Here  04. Need You Now  05. Landslide  06. Golden  07. Stop Draggin' My Heart Around  08. Rhiannon
